<%- include('partials/header') %>

<div style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">
  <h1 style="font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; text-align: center;">About MVP Shopify</h1>
  <div style="aspect-ratio: 16/9; border-radius: var(--radius-lg); overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid var(--border-color); margin-bottom: 2.5rem; background-color: var(--bg-secondary);">
    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/1200x675/1e293b/ffffff?text=Our+Workspace" alt="Workspace" style="width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover;">
  </div>
  
  <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
    Founded in 2026, MVP Shopify is a pilot project designed to showcase state-of-the-art e-commerce architecture. We aim to marry aesthetic user interfaces with strict engineering principles: security-first coding, cryptographic token validation, and real-time shipping carrier API automation.
  </p>
  
  <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
    We believe that modern web applications do not need to compromise speed or safety to look outstanding. By prioritizing server-side input sanitization, data minimization, and secure webhook handshakes, we set a high standard for customer trust.
  </p>

  <div style="margin-top: 3rem; background-color: var(--bg-secondary); border: 1px solid var(--border-color); border-radius: var(--radius-md); padding: 2rem;">
    <h3 style="margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--accent-primary);">Our Core Engineering Values:</h3>
    <ul style="list-style: inside circle; color: var(--text-secondary); display: grid; gap: 0.5rem;">
      <li>Zero-trust third-party API communication.</li>
      <li>Strict constant-time validation signatures for callback handlers.</li>
      <li>Complete separation of critical payment information from our database records.</li>
      <li>Responsive layout aesthetics using fluid grids and custom variables.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</div>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
